WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:01:29.429 --> 00:01:32.256
<i>The fear in her eyes and
the knife in the chest.</i>

3
00:01:32.987 --> 00:01:35.212
<i>That's my last memory of my mother.</i>

4
00:01:35.734 --> 00:01:38.139
<i>That's why I had to go
to prison for four years.</i>

5
00:01:38.239 --> 00:01:39.985
<i>Even though she survived it.</i>

6
00:01:40.826 --> 00:01:42.892
<i>After that it went good for a while.</i>

7
00:01:42.972 --> 00:01:44.896
<i>Until I met that 70 year old.</i>

8
00:01:45.278 --> 00:01:47.362
<i>"Oh my god" were her last words.</i>

9
00:01:47.473 --> 00:01:48.818
<i>Then she was dead.</i>

10
00:01:48.998 --> 00:01:51.224
<i>I didn't know her
and I didn't steal anything.</i>

11
00:01:51.545 --> 00:01:53.569
<i>That damned idea was suddenly there.</i>

12
00:01:53.649 --> 00:01:54.933
<i>I just had to.</i>

13
00:01:55.234 --> 00:01:56.839
<i>I couldn't explain it.</i>

14
00:01:56.978 --> 00:01:59.424
<i>So I went to prison for 10 years.</i>

15
00:02:02.263 --> 00:02:05.391
<i>Then the psychologists got interested
in my inner life.</i>

16
00:02:08.847 --> 00:02:12.577
<i>When they asked me about my dreams.
I told them about flowers.</i>

17
00:02:12.775 --> 00:02:15.163
<i>Flowers.
Always just flowers.</i>

18
00:02:15.925 --> 00:02:19.394
<i>Apart from that. I could fantasize
in my mind whatever I wanted.</i>

19
00:02:19.694 --> 00:02:22.562
<i>It helped me control this urge to...</i>

20
00:02:23.563 --> 00:02:25.690
<i>Just let it all out.</i>

21
00:02:46.663 --> 00:02:50.432
<i>Prison exists so one
can better oneself.</i>

22
00:02:50.894 --> 00:02:56.271
<i>But that urge to torture a human.
that's one thing I never could get rid of.</i>

23
00:03:44.973 --> 00:03:46.517
<i>If you sum everything up.</i>

24
00:03:46.798 --> 00:03:50.227
<i>Then I've been behind bars more than
half of my life.</i>

25
00:03:50.707 --> 00:03:54.697
<i>Only. I never commited a crime
out of pure joy.</i>

26
00:03:55.078 --> 00:03:58.447
<i>There was always a little something.
that was added to it.</i>

27
00:04:55.953 --> 00:04:59.041
<i>I knew. It will happen again.</i>

28
00:04:59.403 --> 00:05:00.726
<i>It has to.</i>

29
00:05:01.007 --> 00:05:03.432
<i>But this time they won't get me.</i>

30
00:05:14.341 --> 00:05:16.205
<i>Nobody came to pick me up.</i>

31
00:05:16.587 --> 00:05:18.912
<i>No family. nothing.</i>

32
00:05:19.655 --> 00:05:21.759
<i>I would've been too excited anyway.</i>

33
00:05:22.461 --> 00:05:25.388
<i>I couldn't sleep the whole last night.</i>

34
00:05:27.550 --> 00:05:29.075
<i>Finally free.</i>

35
00:05:37.696 --> 00:05:40.004
<i>I already had a concrete plan.</i>

36
00:05:40.204 --> 00:05:42.086
<i>The details were all fixed.</i>

37
00:05:42.799 --> 00:05:46.369
<i>Now it was only neccesary to find somebody.</i>

38
00:05:46.911 --> 00:05:49.136
<i>But I didn't know where I was.</i>

39
00:05:49.476 --> 00:05:51.943
<i>I've lived in this town for 10 years.</i>

40
00:05:52.223 --> 00:05:56.454
<i>Only. behind bars you can't get
to know a city.</i>

41
00:05:56.775 --> 00:06:00.044
<i>My first question was: Where to?</i>

42
00:06:00.472 --> 00:06:03.899
<i>I thought: Where can you meet somebody?</i>

43
00:06:04.601 --> 00:06:08.271
<i>So I went to the first Café that was open.</i>

44
00:06:59.762 --> 00:07:02.267
<i>There were two attractive girls
sitting in there.</i>

45
00:07:02.890 --> 00:07:04.794
<i>They were still pretty young.</i>

46
00:07:05.218 --> 00:07:07.134
<i>But that would've worked.</i>

47
00:07:26.690 --> 00:07:30.018
<i>I felt a bit awkward. dressed as I was.</i>

48
00:07:31.203 --> 00:07:34.611
<i>But after 10 years of prison.
you can't be dressed modern.</i>

49
00:07:37.419 --> 00:07:39.383
<i>They stared at me.</i>

50
00:07:44.136 --> 00:07:46.121
<i>I was on it immediately.</i>

51
00:07:56.488 --> 00:07:58.712
<i>They literally provoked me.</i>

52
00:08:01.881 --> 00:08:04.649
<i>My fantasy immediately began to go wild.</i>

53
00:08:34.889 --> 00:08:37.856
<i>I wondered how I could approach them.</i>

54
00:08:38.237 --> 00:08:40.384
<i>That excited me enormously.</i>

55
00:08:40.904 --> 00:08:44.033
<i>I immediately imagined the greatest things.</i>

56
00:08:47.721 --> 00:08:50.269
<i>But it would've caused too much
attention in the Café.</i>

57
00:08:50.450 --> 00:08:52.314
<i>Everyone would have heard us.</i>

58
00:08:52.515 --> 00:08:55.061
<i>That wasn't a good opportunity.</i>

59
00:09:38.872 --> 00:09:42.884
<i>It was absolutely neccesary to find
a quiet place.</i>

60
00:09:44.508 --> 00:09:47.053
<i>And everything would've gone on well.</i>

61
00:09:49.058 --> 00:09:51.365
<i>Then a coincidence helped me.</i>

62
00:10:16.199 --> 00:10:17.783
Where to?

63
00:10:18.239 --> 00:10:20.224
Straigt ahead. please.

64
00:10:22.709 --> 00:10:25.236
<i>The opportunity in the Taxi was great.</i>

65
00:10:25.618 --> 00:10:29.669
<i>It wouldn't be a robbery.
I wasn't interested in money.</i>

66
00:10:37.831 --> 00:10:42.061
<i>That woman reminded me of my
first girlfriend. Anna-Marie.</i>

67
00:10:45.028 --> 00:10:47.075
<i>A real whore.</i>

68
00:10:49.258 --> 00:10:52.828
<i>I was 14 at the time. and she was
significantly older than me.</i>

69
00:10:53.550 --> 00:10:55.575
<i>She nearly could've been my mother.</i>

70
00:10:56.839 --> 00:10:59.324
<i>We sat on a bench in the park.</i>

71
00:11:00.046 --> 00:11:02.212
<i>I had to remove a shoe.</i>

72
00:11:02.587 --> 00:11:05.494
<i>- She took the shoe away from me...</i>
- What are you doing?

73
00:11:06.437 --> 00:11:08.903
<i>She would only return it to me...</i>

74
00:11:09.184 --> 00:11:11.910
<i>...if I gave her a kiss.</i>
- What are you doing there?

75
00:11:12.091 --> 00:11:14.978
<i>Anna-Marie then took me home with her.</i>

76
00:11:15.159 --> 00:11:16.784
<i>She seduced me.</i>

77
00:11:17.024 --> 00:11:19.971
<i>That's when I was able to get active
for the first time.</i>

78
00:11:20.613 --> 00:11:24.083
<i>First I tied her up. then sealed
her mouth shut...</i>

79
00:11:24.502 --> 00:11:26.247
<i>Then I hit her.</i>

80
00:11:26.808 --> 00:11:29.435
<i>With a belt and later with a real whip.</i>

81
00:11:30.618 --> 00:11:32.483
<i>She couldn't get enough.</i>

82
00:11:33.044 --> 00:11:35.230
<i>I really enjoyed it.</i>

83
00:11:35.691 --> 00:11:39.401
<i>I became Anna-Marie's slave.
and it really excited me.</i>

84
00:11:41.133 --> 00:11:42.938
Hey. what are you doing?

85
00:13:52.046 --> 00:13:54.192
<i>Nobody had followed me.</i>

86
00:13:55.255 --> 00:13:59.326
<i>Where to and how long
I'd run. I don't know.</i>

87
00:14:00.328 --> 00:14:02.453
<i>I didn't know that area.</i>

88
00:14:02.814 --> 00:14:04.758
<i>I'd never been there.</i>

89
00:15:40.990 --> 00:15:43.396
<i>The house seemed desolate to me.</i>

90
00:15:44.219 --> 00:15:46.986
<i>I wasn't sure if somebody lived in there.</i>

91
00:16:15.559 --> 00:16:17.706
<i>I noticed no one</i>

92
00:16:18.006 --> 00:16:19.849
<i>and didn't hear anything.</i>

93
00:16:26.413 --> 00:16:28.778
<i>No human soul around.</i>

94
00:16:33.811 --> 00:16:36.918
<i>I thought. that's a paradise for me.</i>

95
00:16:54.244 --> 00:16:57.010
<i>The house was well protected
by the park and the trees.</i>

96
00:16:57.451 --> 00:16:59.938
<i>I didn't have to be afraid
of neighbours here.</i>

97
00:17:00.860 --> 00:17:02.927
<i>The location was perfect.</i>

98
00:17:03.554 --> 00:17:05.778
<i>No danger of being spotted here.</i>

99
00:19:20.501 --> 00:19:22.648
<i>I could hardly breathe.</i>

100
00:19:24.914 --> 00:19:26.799
<i>I was incredibly excited.</i>

101
00:19:35.241 --> 00:19:37.927
<i>The opportunity to meet someone in here...</i>

102
00:19:38.109 --> 00:19:40.093
<i>nearly made me go mad.</i>

103
00:19:46.248 --> 00:19:49.898
<i>I thought I couldn't take it much longer.</i>

104
00:20:35.594 --> 00:20:38.522
<i>I was sure someone lived in here.</i>

105
00:20:41.270 --> 00:20:42.612
<i>My victims.</i>

106
00:20:45.333 --> 00:20:47.117
<i>I was afraid.</i>

107
00:20:51.393 --> 00:20:52.940
Daddy?

108
00:20:55.646 --> 00:20:57.029
<i>Not of the law.</i>

109
00:20:58.373 --> 00:21:03.907
<i>I was in a state of mind that excluded
every kind of logic.</i>

110
00:21:07.777 --> 00:21:10.102
<i>I was afraid of myself.</i>

111
00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:19.687
<i>Already earlier in my life.
I had been in great fear.</i>

112
00:21:20.890 --> 00:21:24.681
<i>For example. as a child it was impossible
for me to be alone in a room.</i>

113
00:21:33.566 --> 00:21:39.562
<i>My grandmother once locked me alone in a
dark room for a whole night.</i>

114
00:21:41.227 --> 00:21:43.672
<i>I thought she was trying to kill me.</i>

115
00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:56.325
<i>That I'd die of fear.</i>

116
00:22:01.680 --> 00:22:03.964
<i>The only thing that helped me
were those sounds.</i>

117
00:22:37.669 --> 00:22:39.316
<i>What luck I had.</i>

118
00:22:39.736 --> 00:22:41.359
<i>What luck I had.</i>

119
00:22:41.681 --> 00:22:43.766
<i>This house was perfect for me.</i>

120
00:22:47.795 --> 00:22:50.040
<i>My plan would work.</i>

121
00:25:55.757 --> 00:25:56.907
Mommy.

122
00:25:57.141 --> 00:25:58.706
Daddy is here.

123
00:25:58.867 --> 00:26:02.114
Don't be stupid. he's long been dead.

124
00:26:39.549 --> 00:26:42.878
<i>As a child. I always had
to fear for my life.</i>

125
00:26:43.982 --> 00:26:47.370
<i>First my mother threw out my father.</i>

126
00:26:52.995 --> 00:26:55.864
<i>Then she lived with another man.</i>

127
00:26:56.523 --> 00:26:58.048
<i>My stepfather.</i>

128
00:26:58.529 --> 00:27:00.934
<i>And she tried to kill me.</i>

129
00:27:01.937 --> 00:27:04.165
<i>She wrapped me in wet diapers</i>

130
00:27:04.324 --> 00:27:06.127
<i>and put me in front of
the open window.</i>

131
00:27:07.010 --> 00:27:10.561
<i>So I should get cold at the window
and freeze to death</i>

132
00:27:17.534 --> 00:27:19.078
Sylvia!

133
00:27:27.873 --> 00:27:29.023
Sylvia...

134
00:27:30.340 --> 00:27:31.490
Sylvia...

135
00:27:49.830 --> 00:27:52.896
<i>I was never safe with my mother.</i>

136
00:27:54.421 --> 00:27:56.447
<i>She hated boys.</i>

137
00:27:59.875 --> 00:28:04.767
<i>For my mother. I was only an attempt
to get a girl.</i>

138
00:28:05.907 --> 00:28:08.153
<i>She didn't want a boy like me.</i>

139
00:28:09.295 --> 00:28:13.326
<i>She developed a real infatuation
for my sister.</i>

140
00:28:25.876 --> 00:28:27.920
<i>I didn't exist for her.</i>

141
00:28:28.722 --> 00:28:32.411
<i>My sister could do with me
whatever she wanted.</i>

142
00:28:46.521 --> 00:28:49.147
<i>My mother always just laughed.</i>

143
00:28:51.374 --> 00:28:54.921
<i>But one time. I caught my sister alone.</i>

144
00:28:56.043 --> 00:28:58.370
<i>I really gave it to her then.</i>

145
00:28:58.891 --> 00:29:00.976
<i>I wanted to hit her until she was dead.</i>

146
00:29:01.157 --> 00:29:04.805
<i>In her eyes I saw
that she was afraid of me.</i>

147
00:29:04.946 --> 00:29:07.572
<i>That excited me enormously.</i>

148
00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:18.333
<i>Because my mother didn't want me.
I grew up at my grandmother's.</i>

149
00:29:20.499 --> 00:29:24.487
<i>But she always just said that she
had to be ashamed of me.</i>

150
00:29:24.990 --> 00:29:27.377
<i>That I was a shame for the whole family.</i>

151
00:29:28.387 --> 00:29:30.491
<i>Because I was an illegitimate child.</i>

152
00:29:40.712 --> 00:29:42.678
<i>She was incredibly religious</i>

153
00:29:43.351 --> 00:29:46.766
<i>...and to purge the guilt.
she sent me to a convent.</i>

154
00:29:50.065 --> 00:29:51.912
<i>I didn't want to.</i>

155
00:29:56.716 --> 00:29:58.996
<i>But I had to become a priest.</i>

156
00:30:37.916 --> 00:30:40.713
<i>We students lived in that convent</i>

157
00:30:41.608 --> 00:30:45.219
<i>...and the nuns and priests
had a farm there.</i>

158
00:30:46.151 --> 00:30:48.316
<i>There were all kinds of animals there.</i>

159
00:30:48.870 --> 00:30:52.860
<i>One afternoon. I secretly
snuck into the barn</i>

160
00:30:53.218 --> 00:30:58.041
<i>...and used a knife until the blood gushed.</i>

161
00:30:59.150 --> 00:31:00.679
<i>It was a pig.</i>

162
00:31:01.255 --> 00:31:07.344
<i>It was afraid of me and squeaked so loudly
that the nuns came and caught me.</i>

163
00:31:34.719 --> 00:31:37.899
<i>After this incident I had to leave
the convent.</i>

164
00:31:40.426 --> 00:31:44.178
<i>For my grandmother. a world collapsed.</i>

165
00:31:44.611 --> 00:31:46.706
<i>She was so religious...</i>

166
00:31:47.673 --> 00:31:50.022
<i>Now I was no longer allowed
to become a priest.</i>

167
00:33:12.305 --> 00:33:15.524
<i>After the incident at the convent.
my mother said</i>

168
00:33:16.235 --> 00:33:18.901
<i>that my family had to be afraid of me.</i>

169
00:33:21.291 --> 00:33:23.839
<i>For her. I now was a monster.</i>

170
00:33:27.106 --> 00:33:30.935
<i>She punished me by not letting
me back to my grandmother.</i>

171
00:33:35.990 --> 00:33:40.256
<i>That was because my stepfather decided
to take over my upbringing.</i>

172
00:33:43.100 --> 00:33:44.906
<i>But he hated me.</i>

173
00:33:46.642 --> 00:33:48.954
<i>He was always good to my sister.</i>

174
00:33:50.732 --> 00:33:53.022
<i>But he couldn't stand me.</i>

175
00:33:53.219 --> 00:33:56.002
<i>She was never treated badly.</i>

176
00:33:57.563 --> 00:34:01.857
<i>One time. he hit me so hard. that I had
to crawl on the floor.</i>

177
00:34:02.823 --> 00:34:07.187
<i>My mother and my sister just stood there
and laughed at me.</i>

178
00:36:14.905 --> 00:36:17.711
<i>I wanted to take revenge on my stepfather.</i>

179
00:36:19.823 --> 00:36:22.587
<i>I wanted to kill him. out of rage.</i>

180
00:36:23.653 --> 00:36:24.937
Daddy.

181
00:36:25.173 --> 00:36:26.991
<i>But I was too weak.</i>

182
00:36:27.248 --> 00:36:28.966
<i>So I had to run away from home.</i>

183
00:36:29.242 --> 00:36:31.236
<i>I slept in the park.</i>

184
00:36:32.353 --> 00:36:34.682
<i>There I observed a swan.</i>

185
00:36:38.968 --> 00:36:41.080
<i>First I strangled it.</i>

186
00:36:41.673 --> 00:36:43.666
<i>Then I cut off its head.</i>

187
00:36:46.994 --> 00:36:51.358
<i>It was expelled from the flock and
didn't go back with them in the water.</i>

188
00:36:52.049 --> 00:36:55.208
<i>It lived all by itself in a corner
of the park.</i>

189
00:36:56.275 --> 00:36:58.190
<i>It liked humans very much.</i>

190
00:36:58.544 --> 00:37:00.539
<i>But it was afraid of me.</i>

191
00:37:01.970 --> 00:37:05.860
<i>I imagined. that I was taking
my revenge then.</i>

192
00:38:02.808 --> 00:38:04.861
<i>Everything went wrong.</i>

193
00:38:08.792 --> 00:38:10.410
<i>Everything happened to fast.</i>

194
00:38:13.827 --> 00:38:16.907
<i>I had it imagined totally differently.</i>

195
00:38:17.208 --> 00:38:19.458
<i>Much much more dramatic.</i>

196
00:38:23.111 --> 00:38:26.745
<i>At least now I wanted to stick to my plan.</i>

197
00:38:27.476 --> 00:38:31.030
<i>First the mother should visit her dead son.</i>

198
00:38:31.808 --> 00:38:33.923
<i>She should observe very carefully</i>

199
00:38:34.060 --> 00:38:36.469
<i>...how he no longer could move.</i>

200
00:38:37.240 --> 00:38:39.471
<i>That would teach her some respect.</i>

201
00:38:43.103 --> 00:38:46.875
<i>But... she wasn't moving anymore herself.</i>

202
00:38:53.129 --> 00:38:56.485
<i>I thought she was playing a trick on me.</i>

203
00:38:56.999 --> 00:38:59.960
<i>Like a fox that pretends to be dead.</i>

204
00:39:03.417 --> 00:39:06.457
<i>I really thought she was pretending.</i>

205
00:39:11.316 --> 00:39:16.409
<i>Then I noticed. there was really
something wrong with her.</i>

206
00:39:23.321 --> 00:39:26.084
<i>Nobody can act that well.</i>

207
00:39:26.697 --> 00:39:28.889
<i>That's impossible.</i>

208
00:39:30.587 --> 00:39:33.273
<i>But she shouldn't be unconscious.</i>

209
00:39:34.141 --> 00:39:36.728
<i>She had to experience every phase
very thoroughly.</i>

210
00:39:47.311 --> 00:39:49.821
<i>I had lost control.</i>

211
00:39:53.651 --> 00:39:55.112
<i>A catastrophe!</i>

212
00:39:56.514 --> 00:39:58.490
<i>That couldn't happen to me.</i>

213
00:39:58.692 --> 00:39:59.842
What are you doing?

214
00:40:01.272 --> 00:40:02.773
Mother is ill.

215
00:40:04.221 --> 00:40:05.799
She needs her medicine...

216
00:40:07.124 --> 00:40:08.782
In the kitchen.

217
00:40:19.800 --> 00:40:22.348
<i>- She could help me.</i>
- Please.

218
00:40:41.511 --> 00:40:44.810
<i>The old one had to stay concscious
no matter what.</i>

219
00:40:45.698 --> 00:40:47.771
<i>I wanted to strangle her after all.</i>

220
00:40:48.522 --> 00:40:53.775
<i>And the daughter should watch
how her mother slowly died.</i>

221
00:40:54.446 --> 00:40:57.744
<i>She should see what it meant to die.</i>

222
00:41:17.202 --> 00:41:19.926
<i>The young one tried to get me.</i>

223
00:41:20.322 --> 00:41:24.685
<i>Either she liked me that much or she
was just trying to rescue herself.</i>

224
00:41:25.021 --> 00:41:28.674
<i>But that didn't matter. she just
didn't know it yet.</i>

225
00:41:35.600 --> 00:41:38.541
<i>I had planned something
very special for her.</i>

226
00:41:38.996 --> 00:41:42.155
<i>She would take the most. that was obvious.</i>

227
00:41:43.044 --> 00:41:46.560
<i>The thing with her is going to be
very special.</i>

228
00:41:47.653 --> 00:41:50.793
<i>In the kitchen I had already noticed
various tools.</i>

229
00:41:52.333 --> 00:41:55.039
<i>With her. I'll do it in the most
precise manner.</i>

230
00:41:55.237 --> 00:41:59.185
<i>Exactly what I had always imagined.</i>

231
00:42:04.883 --> 00:42:07.449
<i>But first I had to wake up the old one.</i>

232
00:42:19.435 --> 00:42:22.278
<i>She had to gain consciousness again.</i>

233
00:42:31.739 --> 00:42:35.214
<i>After all. she was supposed to
whimper and be afraid of me.</i>

234
00:42:40.528 --> 00:42:44.575
<i>Then the daughter would have to watch
how she would die.</i>

235
00:42:55.701 --> 00:42:58.129
<i>She can't give up.</i>

236
00:42:59.927 --> 00:43:01.546
<i>Just like that.</i>

237
00:43:03.638 --> 00:43:05.752
<i>I finished her.</i>

238
00:43:16.141 --> 00:43:19.221
<i>Now only the girl was left to me.</i>

239
00:43:47.770 --> 00:43:48.920
You!

240
00:43:52.766 --> 00:43:53.916
You.

241
00:44:13.461 --> 00:44:14.611
You.

242
00:44:48.800 --> 00:44:49.950
You.

243
00:45:03.748 --> 00:45:06.235
You... You.

244
00:52:38.925 --> 00:52:42.698
<i>I didn't want to leave the corpses in
the house like that.</i>

245
00:55:40.242 --> 00:55:45.179
<i>I decided to take the family with me.</i>

246
00:55:53.521 --> 00:55:57.209
<i>The thought that I could have
the corpses with me all the time</i>

247
00:55:57.360 --> 00:55:59.819
<i>...excited me tremendously.</i>

248
00:56:15.893 --> 00:56:18.638
<i>In no case would I leave without them.</i>

249
00:56:19.645 --> 00:56:23.317
<i>I had my plans with the corpses.</i>

250
00:56:47.882 --> 00:56:52.938
<i>I was determined that this all was only
the beginning.</i>

251
00:56:54.101 --> 00:56:57.854
<i>I wanted to live out my fantasies.</i>

252
00:56:58.347 --> 00:57:02.514
<i>At that moment. I didn't care where that
would lead.</i>

253
00:57:03.559 --> 00:57:05.871
<i>I didn't think about it at all.</i>

254
00:57:06.266 --> 00:57:09.209
<i>I wanted to get new victims
as soon as possible.</i>

255
00:57:09.701 --> 00:57:11.854
<i>I was crazy about it.</i>

256
00:57:12.704 --> 00:57:15.823
<i>I made a new plan.</i>

257
00:57:20.819 --> 00:57:24.037
<i>I wanted to show the corpses to
the new victims.</i>

258
00:57:24.531 --> 00:57:28.894
<i>I was convinced that I could really scare
them with that.</i>

259
00:57:34.721 --> 00:57:39.973
<i>I had the idea that I would lock the new
victims together with the corpses.</i>

260
00:57:44.810 --> 00:57:47.773
<i>That would scare them enormously.</i>

261
00:57:48.524 --> 00:57:51.346
<i>Some would surely die of fear.</i>

262
00:57:51.979 --> 00:57:56.085
<i>They couldn't stand being tortured that way.</i>

263
00:58:02.063 --> 00:58:04.944
<i>And then I would finish them off.</i>

264
01:06:09.493 --> 01:06:12.257
<i>After the act I felt very well.</i>

265
01:06:13.100 --> 01:06:15.113
<i>My head felt lighter.</i>

266
01:06:17.056 --> 01:06:19.664
<i>Also my whole body felt lighter.</i>

267
01:06:20.077 --> 01:06:23.257
<i>I thought that everything I did was
easier now.</i>

268
01:06:24.245 --> 01:06:26.179
<i>As if I was floating.</i>

269
01:06:34.384 --> 01:06:38.827
<i>I was in a bright. yes even cheerful mood.</i>

270
01:06:47.200 --> 01:06:49.965
<i>Of course I knew that this state of mind...</i>

271
01:06:50.203 --> 01:06:53.025
<i>...this relief. wouldn't last long.</i>

272
01:06:53.657 --> 01:06:56.421
<i>That the urge would return.</i>

273
01:08:56.385 --> 01:08:57.628
Hey!

274
01:08:57.924 --> 01:08:59.346
Hey!

275
01:08:59.583 --> 01:09:01.993
Hey. get out of there!

276
01:09:02.307 --> 01:09:05.073
Get out of there already!

277
01:09:07.481 --> 01:09:08.903
Hey!

278
01:09:10.877 --> 01:09:12.694
Come on!

279
01:11:07.733 --> 01:11:10.694
<i>I can't pity the victims.</i>

280
01:11:11.455 --> 01:11:13.094
<i>I wanted to continue to murder.</i>

281
01:11:24.925 --> 01:11:27.491
<i>I already had a perfect plan.</i>

282
01:12:29.589 --> 01:12:32.256
<i>The two girls were sitting there again.</i>

283
01:12:33.164 --> 01:12:34.921
<i>I was on it immediately.</i>

284
01:12:48.651 --> 01:12:52.048
<i>My fantasy immediately began to go wild.</i>

285
01:13:02.196 --> 01:13:04.072
<i>It was irresistible.</i>

286
01:13:04.803 --> 01:13:06.362
<i>Just fantastic.</i>

287
01:13:17.593 --> 01:13:19.430
<i>I thought...</i>

288
01:13:20.871 --> 01:13:23.084
<i>How could I approach them?</i>

289
01:13:28.158 --> 01:13:29.640
<i>Then I decided...</i>

290
01:13:29.995 --> 01:13:32.028
<i>I'll take them all.</i>

291
01:13:41.665 --> 01:13:44.745
<i>I'll take all four of them
right now. right here.</i>

292
01:15:18.401 --> 01:15:20.000
Show me your registration.

293
01:15:21.658 --> 01:15:23.870
I don't have anything to do it with!

294
01:15:28.860 --> 01:15:30.203
The registration!

295
01:15:30.500 --> 01:15:34.033
I got the car from someone else.
I don't know how that happened.

296
01:15:34.152 --> 01:15:36.503
- I don't care. show me your registration!
- I...

297
01:15:36.681 --> 01:15:38.102
What now?

298
01:15:38.615 --> 01:15:43.570
- Do you have a registration or don't you?
- It's not my fault. that's not my car...

299
01:15:45.599 --> 01:15:47.850
I don't care. show me your registration.

300
01:15:48.146 --> 01:15:50.396
<i>The moment was very thrilling.</i>

301
01:15:51.483 --> 01:15:53.517
<i>It really excited me.</i>

302
01:15:53.971 --> 01:15:57.492
- But I don't have anything to do with it!
- Open up the trunk!

303
01:15:57.762 --> 01:16:00.565
<i>Now everybody's going
to be scared to death.</i>

304
01:16:04.293 --> 01:16:06.605
<i>Now everybody is afraid of me.</i>

305
01:16:07.079 --> 01:16:08.814
<i>I'm famous.</i>

306
01:16:09.526 --> 01:16:11.758
<i>It's a pity about those girls. though...</i>

307
01:16:11.936 --> 01:16:14.225
<i>That would've been a nice tango.</i>

308
01:16:18.994 --> 01:16:22.116
<i>Excerpt from the psychiatric opinion.</i>

309
01:16:22.746 --> 01:16:26.083
<i>"The patient planned and commited
the crime consciously</i>

310
01:16:26.242 --> 01:16:31.000
<i>to gain physical satisfaction.</i>

311
01:16:31.671 --> 01:16:35.107
<i>His personality is liable and perverse.</i>

312
01:16:35.482 --> 01:16:39.667
<i>The worst mental disorder
is a pronounced sadism.</i>

313
01:16:40.063 --> 01:16:43.696
<i>However mental illness wasn't the diagnoses.</i>

314
01:16:44.388 --> 01:16:46.757
<i>That by hurting somebody and by
using violence...</i>

315
01:16:46.935 --> 01:16:50.982
<i>on other people. he could get
sexually excited</i>

316
01:16:51.259 --> 01:16:54.575
<i>this was known to the patient since
early childhood.</i>

317
01:16:55.306 --> 01:16:58.486
<i>His relation to society
is severly disturbed.</i>

318
01:16:58.881 --> 01:17:05.081
<i>This is because as a baby he was
abandoned by the mother</i>

319
01:17:05.219 --> 01:17:09.563
<i>and later would never know a stable family.</i>

320
01:17:09.919 --> 01:17:12.654
<i>The patient is one hundred percent
responsible</i>

321
01:17:13.047 --> 01:17:17.333
<i>but one cannot speak of guilt in
the common sense with this case.</i>

322
01:17:17.729 --> 01:17:21.479
<i>The prospect of punishment
didn't stop him from murdering."</i>

323
01:17:22.625 --> 01:17:25.172
<i>Sentence on behalf of the people:</i>

324
01:17:25.564 --> 01:17:28.190
<i>Imprisonment for life.</i>

324
